Document: RenderSceneBuffersExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_renderscenebuffersextension.rst
Summary: Private methods for configuring viewport resizing, anisotropic filtering, FSR sharpness, texture mipmap bias, and debanding in a render scene buffer extension.

Method: _configure(RenderSceneBuffersConfiguration config) → void. Virtual method. Implement this in GDExtension to handle the (re)sizing of a viewport.
Method: _set_anisotropic_filtering_level(int anisotropic_filtering_level) → void. Virtual method. Implement this in GDExtension to change the anisotropic filtering level.
Method: _set_fsr_sharpness(float fsr_sharpness) → void. Virtual method. Implement this in GDExtension to record a new FSR sharpness value.
Method: _set_texture_mipmap_bias(float texture_mipmap_bias) → void. Virtual method. Implement this in GDExtension to change the texture mipmap bias.
Method: _set_use_debanding(bool use_debanding) → void. Virtual method. Implement this in GDExtension to react to the debanding flag changing.